profile:
At Home Style Electric we do our very best to make sure that we cover all of your electrical needs. When you need professional residential electrical services, no job is too big or too small for Home Style Electric. Our staff is friendly, trustworthy, professional and knowledgeable, so you're in good hands.  Home Style Electric has a solid reputation for quality work and efficient service at a fair price. We take great pride in that fact that many of our customers hear about us by word of mouth and referrals from their friends.

You can trust Home Style Electric for all of your residential electrical needs whether it is a small job such as repairing an outlet or hanging a fixture to a larger job such as a panel change or an electrical service upgrade. Home Style Electric is able to provide you with the peace of mind of knowing that your electrical needs are being met by a qualified journeyman electrician.

No job is too insignificant for Home Style Electric.  In fact, we built the company concentrating on the little jobs that other companies wouldn't take the time to do.  Just some of the services we offer include:


Panel Changes
Pot light installations
Electrical Service Upgrades
Aluminum Wiring remediation (also referred to as Pig Tailing)
Surge Protection
Trouble Shooting
Lighting Installations
Fan Installations
Hot Tub wiring
Outdoor Lighting
Dealing with issues raised by home Inspectors  (buying or selling)
New Wiring
Garage Wiring
Kitchen Renovations
Bathroom Renovations
